obiety), is committed to facilitating and improving the accessibility and usability of its Website, www.highsnobiety.com.\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2607, \"end\": 2612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titel\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titel\"}, {\"begin\": 2619, \"end\": 2623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gesellschaft_mit_beschr\\u00e4nkter_Haftung\", \"score\": 0.9993142668117073, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"GmbH\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gesellschaft_mit_beschr\\u00e4nkter_Haftung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gesellschaft_mit_beschr\\u00e4nkter_Haftung\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Highsnobiety\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"the accessibility\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2700}, {\"ngram\": \"usability\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\": \"its Website\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Titel Media GmbH strives to ensure that its Website services and content are accessible to persons with disabilities including users of screen reader technology.\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2753, \"end\": 2758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titel\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titel\"}, {\"begin\": 2765, \"end\": 2769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gesellschaft_mit_beschr\\u00e4nkter_Haftung\", \"score\": 0.9993142668117073, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"GmbH\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gesellschaft_mit_beschr\\u00e4nkter_Haftung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gesellschaft_mit_beschr\\u00e4nkter_Haftung\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"n