 3176, \"to\": 3187}, {\"ngram\": \"accessibility\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3213}, {\"ngram\": \"usability\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While we strive to make the Website as accessible as possible some issues can be encountered by different assistive technology as the range of assistive technology is wide and varied.\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Website\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3276}, {\"ngram\": \"some issues\", \"from\": 3303, \"to\": 3314}, {\"ngram\": \"different assistive technology\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3367}, {\"ngram\": \"the range\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3380}, {\"ngram\": \"assistive technology\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If, at any time, you have specific questions or concerns about the accessibility of any particular webpage on this Website, please contact us at accessibility@highsnobiety.com, +49 (0)30 235 908 500.\", \"from\": 3426, \"to\": 3625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3441}, {\"ngram\": \"specific questions\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3470}, {\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3482}, {\"ngram\": \"the accessibility\", \"from\": 3489, \"to\": 3506}, {\"ngram\": \"any particular webpage\", \"from\": 3510, \"to\": 3532}, {\"ngram\": \"this Website\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3548}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3565, \"to\": 3567}, {\"ngram\": \"+49\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3606}, {\"ngram\": \"0)30\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3612}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you do encounter an accessibility issue, please be sure to specify the web page and nature of the issue in your email and/or phone call, and we will make all reasonable efforts to make that page or the information contained therein accessible for you.\", \"from\": 3626, \"to\": 3880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an accessibility issue\", \"from\": 3646, \"to\": 3668}, {\"ngram\": \"the web page\", \"from\": 3696, \"to\": 3708}, {\"ngram\": \"nature\", \"from\": 3713, \"to\": 3719}, {\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 3723, \"to\": 3732}, {\"ngram\": \"your email and/or phone call\", \"from\": 3736, \"to\": 3764}, {\"ngram\": \"all reasonable efforts\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3805}, {\"ngram\": \"that page\", \"from\": 3814, \"to\": 3823}, {\"ngram\": \"the information\", \"from\": 3827, \"to\": 3842}]}]}"